xdm:num.title: Session Number
xdm:num.description: Current session number for the end-user.

xdm:depth.title: Session Depth
xdm:depth.description: Current session depth (eg page number) for the end-user.

xdm:timestamp.title: Session Entry Timestamp
xdm:timestamp.description: The timestamp at the entry into this session. Milliseconds since midnight of January 1, 1970.

xdm:search.title: Session Entry Search
xdm:search.description: The information related to web or mobile search at the entry of this session.

xdm:web.title: Session Entry Web
xdm:web.description: Link clicks, web page details, referrer information, and browser details.
